    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Ask AI for  Cleaning Tips\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to clean a messy data entry and compare its approach to yours.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n**Do This:**\r\n\r\n1. Ask AI Chat:\r\n   - *How would you clean this messy pizza topping entry: \"don’t like pepperonni but i'll eat peproni if itz there\"?*\r\n   - *Should this entry be deleted or changed? Why?*\r\n2. Review AI Chat’s answer.\r\n3. Compare it to your own decision and your partner's.\r\n",
